subject: Rose Bowl (Football Game)
Football (College)
lead_paragraph: Michigan State’s victory against Stanford hinged on Connor Cook, a quarterback who started the season as a backup, and Kyler Elsworth, a linebacker who arrived on campus as a walk-on.
